<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>맞춤법/발음 교정 서비스</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      * {
        font-family: "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50">
    <!-- 네비게이션 바 -->
    <nav class="bg-white shadow-lg">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-16">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">굿플랜트</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <a href="/login" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900"
              >로그인</a
            >
            <a href="/register" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900"
              >회원가입</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 메인 섹션 -->
    <div class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">
          맞춤법 / 말하기<br />태도 개선 도우미
        </h1>
        <p class="text-center text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          AI가 실시간으로 분석하고 교정해드립니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center">
          <a
            href="/correction"
            class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md"
            >시작하기</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 기능 소개 -->
    <div class="bg-white py-12">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">주요 기능</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/spelling-check">
              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-500 text-white mx-auto"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-spell-check"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
                맞춤법 검사
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                AI가 문맥을 고려하여 정확한 맞춤법을 제안합니다.
              </p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <!-- 발음 교정 -->
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/pronunciation-check">
              <!-- 링크 추가 -->
              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-500 text-white mx-auto"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">발음 교정</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                실시간으로 발음을 분석하고 개선점을 제안합니다.
              </p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/history">
              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-blue-500 text-white mx-auto"
              >
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="mt-5 text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">교정 이력</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-500">
                교정된 이력을 한눈에 알아볼 수 있습니다.
              </p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 푸터 -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 py-8">
      <div class="text-center text-gray-400">
        <p>&copy; 2024 맞춤법/발음 교정 서비스. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
